        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 27,
        "end": 34
      },
      {
        "text": "乃于晉州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 35,
        "end": 39
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000090",
    "sentence": "至是到行在，皆賜分物衣服，放歸本道，以示懷服。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000091",
