    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000128",
    "sentence": "是日，降雪盈尺，帝升壇而雪霽。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000129",
    "sentence": "禮畢，禦五鳳樓，宣制大赦天下。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000130",
    "sentence": "賜南郊行事官禮儀使趙光逢以下分物。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000131",
    "sentence": "甲午，上御文思殿宴群臣，賜金帛有差。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_004_000132",
